3] Variable = variable memory location er nam, variavle er modde jei value ta raka hove sei value ta ram er jei slot e takve oi slot er nam ta variabler er nam e defind hoye jave

             Variable declaration major rules = 3 major rules for create variable for java script
                              1] start with var sign
                              2](a-z) ,(A-Z), (0-9), (_), ($) ,
                              3] No Number in first

             Variable declaration Standerd rules = 3 Standerd rules for create variable for java script
                                          1] small letter
                                          2] meaningFulll
                                          3] readable

 4] Nam leker Standerd=========
                        * variable = firstName / first    {Kemel Case}
                        * input fild = first_name / first {Zen}
                        * Folder = first-name / first
                        * file = first-name / first
                        * Id = firstName / first          {Kemel Case}

